high_descs: Turn to the right and move to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up the apple from the counter above the knife
Turn to the table on the left
Put the apple in the bowl
Turn to the small black table to the right
Pick up the knife from the table
Turn left towards the white table
Slice the apple in the bowl
Put the knife in the bowl with the apple
pick up the bowl with the apple and knife
Turn around and move to the fridge to the left
Open the fridge, place the bowl with the apple and knife inside then close the fridge door
anns.task_desc: Preparing an apple and putting it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right towards the table. Make another right to face the counter.
Pick up apple from counter.
Turn to the left with the apple.
Place the apple inside the bowl on the table.
Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife from the side table.
Turn to the left and face the counter.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Put the knife inside the bowl with the apple slices.
Pick up the bowl with everything inside.
Turn completely around and walk to the fridge. Make a left to face it.
Open the fridge and place the bowl, knife, and apple slices inside. Shut the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, place in the fridge with bowl and knife.

high_descs: Turn all the way around then walk towards the table, turn right then head towards the sink.
Pick up the golden apple from the counter top.
Turn left towards the table.
Place the golden apple into the square dish in between two salt shakers.
Turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the knife behind the white bottle on the top shelf of the black cabinet.
Turn left then towards the table.
Slice the golden apple inside the square dish on the table.
Place the knife inside the dish with the apple.
Pick up the square dish from the table.
Turn around then walk towards the refrigerator.
Place the dish on the top shelf in the refrigerator, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife and a sliced apple inside a square dish in the refrigerator.
